My Wife & I had a Whiting Dinner with Collard Greens & Potato Salad & it was banging/ on thee money, We love it, also had a catfish sandwich we we also rate a 10. The food is great, the quantity is good, Hospitality great & the price is right. If you have not ever been to Crockett s, We recommend you get on over there, you will not be disappointed, We will be back very soon, to try other items on there menu, which we already know will be a blast. Our Hats go off to Crockett for there many years of success & we pray for many more yrs to come.   A great place  & a Great experience.AS the record states , Lets do it again, & we will.
